  <!-- ======= 11. Principles ======= -->
  <section class="slide" id="slide-11">
    <div class="slide__inner">
      <p class="hs-section-num">07</p>
      <h2 class="slide__heading">Principles</h2>
      <div class="hs-principle-grid">
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Consequence, not beauty</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">The draw is to places where people do real things in the presence of forces that could end it. Shepherds near borders. Craftspeople in economies industrializing past them. The photographs follow the consequence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Essentialism</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">The disciplined pursuit of less. Every image in a sequence, every design decision, every word on the page earns its place or gets cut. Good enough is valid when stated with criteria.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Systems, not surfaces</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">Think in tradeoffs and constraints. The site is a system. The brand is architecture. The sequencing of a collection is a design problem. &ldquo;What&rsquo;s the actual constraint here?&rdquo; before every decision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Embodied practice</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">The camera follows the life, not the other way around. Walking as method. Skin tracks before dawn, ridge runs in August. Knowledge is felt before it&rsquo;s parsed. The work comes from the body, not the desk.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Precision is warmth</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">Getting the details right is how you show respect. Name the lens, the place, the hour. Directness is care&mdash;softening wastes time. Profundity arrives in workwear, not formal dress. No emojis. No filler. Ever.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hs-principle">
          <div class="hs-principle__title">Natural &amp; technical</div>
          <p class="hs-principle__text">Earth tones layered with technical materials. Lived-in quality developing patina over time. Markdown that doesn&rsquo;t disappear, self-hosted on infrastructure you control. Own the platform. Own the archive.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

